            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1190558132" class="vote-count">5</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1190558132" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1190558132">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/Radioeye2000/">Someone/</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2017-05-15</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">I think this book describe perfectly that the Hollywood film makers&#39; life was unique and can&#39;t be forget all the time.The World War II destroyed culture and &#34;built&#34; a whole new culture with the film world from this moment. Just watch the book then&#39; would know why these films and Hollywood can be this charming and discover film-at-War time.</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1173846005">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1173846005" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1173846005" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1173846005">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/charlottes-web/">Charlotte&#39;sWeb</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2017-05-28</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">磅礴的时代群像传记。没想到Stevens团队在战争后期和纽伦堡审判中作为证据收集者，在地狱走了一遭。留守的Capra挣扎寻找自己的政治理念，作品的模糊性和天真妥协原来是公认的啊……It&#39;s a wonderful life作为失败的注脚结束全篇，多年后被重新推为代表作（我也好喜欢！）Wyler对飞行的执着留下身体的创伤，但是却打开了现实主义的探索。Ford和Houston的个人英雄感还真是和印象中高度吻合……对于战争影像的重演还是实拍的矛盾。军队宣传部权力的撕扯。梅利特对国际主义的强调和对敌人简单化种族主义的警惕。从38年到45年，战争从不受欢迎的阴影变成了主流映像又变成避之不及的回响。二十世纪的伤疤。翻译总是出现前后片名不一致orz</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
